control_data.kq_imcx.control:
# This file is generated content from add_postgresql_extension.
# No point in modifying it, it will be overwritten anyway.

# Default version, always set
default_version = '0.1'

# Module pathname generated from target shared library name. Use
# MODULE_PATHNAME in script file.
module_pathname = '$libdir/kq_imcx.so'

# Comment for extension. Set using COMMENT option. Can be set in
# script file as well.
comment = 'ketteQ In-Memory Calendar Extension (IMCX)'

# Encoding for script file. Set using ENCODING option.
#encoding = ''

# Required extensions. Set using REQUIRES option (multi-valued).
#requires = ''
trusted = true

control_data.weighted_mean.control:
# weighted_mean extension
comment = 'A weighted mean aggregate function extension'
default_version = '1.0.1'
module_pathname = '$libdir/weighted_mean'
relocatable = true
trusted = true

control_data.anon.control:
# PostgreSQL Anonymizer (anon) extension
comment = 'Data anonymization tools'
default_version = '1.1.0'
directory='extension/anon'
relocatable = false
requires = 'pgcrypto'
superuser = false
module_pathname = '$libdir/anon'
trusted = true
